text: Arantzazu Azpiroz (born 1 September 1981) is a road cyclist from Spain. She represented her nation at the 2002 and 2007 UCI Road World Championships. ==References== ==External links== * profile at Procyclingstats.com Category:1981 births Category:Spanish female cyclists Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
